---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
import Hero from '../components/molecules/Hero.astro';
import Button from '../components/atoms/Button.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="Sell Your Helicopter" description="Sell your helicopter to Aviaco France - Part 145 maintenance centre specialized in dismantling and repurposing helicopter parts">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <Hero 
    title="Sell your helicopter" 
    image="/copter/1.jpg"
    imageAlt="Helicopter for sale"
  />

  <!-- Introduction Section -->
  <section class="py-12 md:py-16 lg:py-20 bg-white dark:bg-gray-900">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="font-outfit font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl mb-5 md:mb-6 lg:mb-8 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
          Elevating your helicopter sale to a strategic financial move
        </h2>
        <p class="font-outfit text-base md:text-lg lg:text-xl text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-5 md:mb-6">
          When it is time to part ways with your trusted helicopter, Aviaco France is the first choice for a financial decision. As a Part 145 maintenance centre, Aviaco France is specialised in the dismantling and repurposing of helicopter parts, ensuring that each component finds a new life in other aircraft.
        </p>
        <p class="font-outfit text-base md:text-lg lg:text-xl text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-5 md:mb-6">
          Take the first step towards selling your helicopter today by submitting your proposal to Aviaco.
        </p>
        <p class="font-outfit text-base md:text-lg lg:text-xl text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
          With our pledge of paying the right price, you will not only maximise the value of your sale, but you will also contribute to a thriving secondary market, keeping our operational costs down for helicopter operators worldwide. By choosing Aviaco France, you are not only selling an helicopter; you are participating in a smart financial transaction that benefits the entire aviation industry.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Image Section -->
  <section class="py-8 md:py-10 lg:py-12 bg-white dark:bg-gray-900">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="aspect-square w-full overflow-hidden rounded-xl shadow-2xl">
          <img 
            src="/copter/2.jpg" 
            alt="Helicopter dismantling" 
            class="w-full h-full object-cover"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Sustainability Section -->
  <section class="py-12 md:py-16 lg:py-20 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800/50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 md:gap-8 lg:gap-12 items-center">
          <div>
            <h2 class="font-outfit font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl mb-5 md:mb-6 lg:mb-8 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
              Pioneering sustainable aviation solutions
            </h2>
            <p class="font-outfit text-base md:text-lg lg:text-xl text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-5 md:mb-6">
              In an era where environmental consciousness is of the greatest importance, selling your helicopter to Aviaco France is a testament to your commitment to sustainability and participation to a circular economy. Our helicopter parts dismantling process follows the highest environment standards, demonstrated by our many CSR labels and certifications.
            </p>
            <p class="font-outfit text-base md:text-lg lg:text-xl text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
              With a focus on minimising waste and reducing the ecological footprint of aviation, Aviaco France contributes to the reduction of unnecessary manufacturing and the conservation of resources. This eco-friendly approach aligns with the global efforts to protect our planet and sets a new era for the aviation's circular economy with a responsible end-of-life aircraft management for a sustainable aviation industry.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-8 md:mt-0">
            <div class="aspect-square w-full overflow-hidden rounded-xl shadow-xl">
              <img 
                src="/copter/9.jpg" 
                alt="Sustainable aviation" 
                class="w-full h-full object-cover"
                loading="lazy"
              />
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Impact Section -->
  <section class="py-12 md:py-16 lg:py-20 bg-white dark:bg-gray-900">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 md:gap-8 lg:gap-12 items-center">
          <div class="order-2 md:order-1 mt-8 md:mt-0">
            <div class="aspect-square w-full overflow-hidden rounded-xl shadow-xl">
              <img 
                src="/copter/10.jpg" 
                alt="Helicopter parts" 
                class="w-full h-full object-cover"
                loading="lazy"
              />
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="order-1 md:order-2">
            <h2 class="font-outfit font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl mb-5 md:mb-6 lg:mb-8 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
              Elevating the skies, one helicopter part at a time
            </h2>
            <p class="font-outfit text-base md:text-lg lg:text-xl text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
              The decision to sell your helicopter to Aviaco France has many implications beyond immediate financial gain. Each part we salvage from your aircraft plays a crucial role in keeping dozens of helicopters airborne. This commitment ensures the longevity and safety of helicopter fleets across the globe. By supporting the aviation industry and its missions, you will contribute to saving lives and keep up the economy.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Partnership Section -->
  <section class="py-12 md:py-16 lg:py-20 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800/50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="font-outfit font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl mb-5 md:mb-6 lg:mb-8 text-gray-900 dark:text-white text-center">
          Your aviation partner for a sustainable future
        </h2>
        <p class="font-outfit text-base md:text-lg lg:text-xl text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-5 md:mb-6 text-center">
          More than a maintenance centre; Aviaco France aims to be your partner in the aviation journey. By selling your helicopter to us, you will join a network of professionals dedicated to the advancement and sustainability of the helicopter industry.
        </p>
        <p class="font-outfit text-base md:text-lg lg:text-xl text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed text-center">
          We take pride in our transparent and efficient selling process, offering high quality spare parts at competitive prices which insure long-lasting relationships with our partners. With Aviaco France, you are not just parting ways with your helicopter, but you are taking part in an international network that keeps the helicopters flying and support the future of aviation.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-12 md:py-16 lg:py-20 bg-gray-900 dark:bg-black text-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h2 class="font-outfit font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl mb-5 md:mb-6 lg:mb-8">
          Ready to sell your helicopter?
        </h2>
        <p class="font-outfit text-base md:text-lg lg:text-xl text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-8 md:mb-10">
          Take the first step towards a strategic financial move. Contact us today to submit your proposal and discover how Aviaco France can maximize the value of your helicopter sale.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <Button href="/contact" variant="secondary" size="lg" class="shadow-2xl">
            Submit your proposal
          </Button>
          <Button href="/exchange" variant="outline" size="lg" class="!bg-transparent !border-2 !border-white !text-white hover:!bg-white hover:!text-gray-900 !transition-all">
            Learn about exchange
          </Button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>
